title: Mindy Sperry Elected President of Downtown Kansas City Kiwanis Club (Arvest Bank Group Inc)
text: ( Source : Arvest Bank Group Inc) Mindy Sperry, Arvest Branch Manager in the greater Kansas City area, was recently elected president of the Downtown Kansas City Kiwanis Club * for 2015-2016. She was honored at the installation of officers
